## Write a program to convert inches to feet

1 foot = 12 inches

```
Input  : 60
Output : 5
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-inches-to-feet" >

```cpp
#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int inches;
    cin>>inches;
    int foot=(int)inches/12;
    cout<<foot<<'\n';
    return 0;
}
```

```java
